text: Noelani Day (born 24 April 2003) is a Tongan swimmer. She competed in the women's 50 metre freestyle at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships and she finished in 67th place. ==References== Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Tongan female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female freestyle swimmers
